      "content": "thanks for looking at this. i've already added the null checks like you suggested, but the error is still popping up occasionally in the logs. it's almost like it's totally random. like, sometimes it works fine, and then suddenly it just breaks for no reason. any idea why it would feel so unpredictable?",
